Maths

My advisors are Masoud Kamgarpour and Ole Warnaar.

My CV is here and my GitHub is here.

I am interested in representation theory, geometry, and computational mathematics, often using the Chevie package for Julia.

My masters thesis was about the Arithmetic Geometry of Character Varieties.

For a visual explanation, I created a poster about the Topology of Representation Spaces via Arithmetic.

My undergraduate thesis was about Hecke Algebras and Gelfand Pairs in Representation Theory.
